  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe understand the importance of supporting you during pregnancy, childbirth, and related medical conditions. This policy outlines the availability of paid pregnancy disability benefits, which provide income replacement during periods of temporary disability due to pregnancy. These benefits are provided in accordance with applicable federal and state laws and may coordinate with other leave entitlements. We are committed to ensuring you receive the support needed during this significant life event.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
